channel.title: The Great Food Guys
channel.desc: Nick Nairn and Dougie Vipond embrace spices, cooking beef fajitas with refried beans, pico de galo and guacamole on a homemade tortilla. Their special guest is comedian Bruce Fummey, who joins them in the kitchen for a chat and to try this week's food and drink.
